<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Email Verification - Supag</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .code { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Email Verification</h1>
        </div>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering with Supag!</p>
        
        <p>To complete your registration, please use the following verification code:</p>
        
        <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
        
        <p>If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Supag Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 